foods.description: MOOSEHEAD LAKE FUDGE PEANUT BUTTER FILLED CUPS IN CHOCOLATE REDUCED FAT ICE CREAM WITH A THICK FUDGE SWIRL, MOOSEHEAD LAKE FUDGE
